# ðŸš¨ Helmet Violation Detection System

A real-time helmet violation detection system built using **YOLOv8**, **Streamlit**, and **PaddleOCR**.

This app detects:
- Motorcyclists **without helmets** within a defined zone
- Automatically captures and **logs number plates** of violators

---

## ðŸ”§ Features

- ðŸŽ¥ **Live Detection** via Webcam or Uploaded Video  
- ðŸ§  **YOLOv8** for detecting helmets and number plates  
- ðŸ”¤ **PaddleOCR** for number plate recognition  
- ðŸ—ºï¸ Polygonal **Zone-based detection**  
- ðŸ“ Fine Logging:
  - Vehicle number  
  - Date and Time  
  - Snapshot of number plate  
- ðŸ“ Export fines as CSV  
- ðŸ“¸ Image preview of captured plates  

---

## ðŸ–¥ï¸ Interface (Streamlit)

- **Sidebar**: View Violation History  
- **Main View**:
  - Live/resumed video feed  
  - Real-time fine log table  
  - Number plate image gallery  
  - Download fine log as CSV  

